{"title":"Debian10的网络配置","uid":"63c71fba5e8a34529d9bdb3a5facfcb9","slug":"Debian10的网络配置","date":"2022-07-21T04:58:59.000Z","updated":"2022-07-21T05:01:07.494Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Debian10的网络配置.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><h2 id=\"网络配置\"><a href=\"#网络配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网络配置\"></a>网络配置</h2><h4 id=\"一、配置文件方式\"><a href=\"#一、配置文件方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、配置文件方式\"></a>一、配置文件方式</h4><p>1、编辑网卡配置文件interfaces</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;network&#x2F;interfaces\n... \nauto ens33\niface ens33 inet static address\naddress 172.16.100.201&#x2F;25\ngateway 172.16.100.254\n\n#auto ens33 启动服务的时候激活网卡，ens33为网卡名称\n#iface ens33 inet static 接口属性配置，支持static（静态）、dhcp（动态)、none（默认）模式 \n#address，IP地址配置，支持IP&#x2F;PREFIX方式 \n#netmask，掩码 \n#gateway，网关地址</code></pre>\n\n<p>2、重启网络服务</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">systemctl restart networking\nsystemctl restart network-manager</code></pre>\n\n\n\n","text":"网络配置一、配置文件方式1、编辑网卡配置文件interfaces vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;network&#x2F;interfaces ... auto ens33 iface ens33 inet static address address 172.16.10...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":419,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Debian","slug":"Debian","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Debian.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Debian","slug":"Debian","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Debian.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">网络配置</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E9%85%8D%E7%